6 HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
7 132ND LEGISLATURE
8 FIRST SPECIAL SESSION
9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 882, L.D. 1359, “Resolve, to Direct the
10 Department of Transportation to Develop Practices Regarding Public Transit”
11 Amend the resolve by striking out the title and substituting the following:
12 'Resolve, to Direct the Department of Transportation to Report Progress Made
13 Toward Implementing Recommendations Based on the 2025 Public Transit Advisory
14 Council Report'
15 Amend the resolve by striking out everything after the title and inserting the following:
16 'Sec. 1. Implementation progress; report. Resolved: That, by December 3,
17 2025, the Department of Transportation shall submit to the Joint Standing Committee on
18 Transportation a report detailing the department's progress on implementing the
19 recommendations from the 2025 Public Transit Advisory Council report pursuant to the
20 Maine Revised Statutes, Title 23, section 4209-A, subsection 5. The report must include,
21 but is not limited to, a summary of actions taken toward implementing each
22 recommendation to the department from the Public Transit Advisory Council report,
23 including specific dates on which those actions were taken; a list of specific dates on which
24 the department plans to take additional actions toward implementing each
25 recommendation; and a list of recommendations not yet implemented. The Joint Standing
26 Committee on Transportation may report out legislation to the Second Regular Session of
27 the 132nd Legislature based on the report.'
28 Amend the resolve by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or
29 section number to read consecutively.
30 SUMMARY
3311 This amendment replaces the resolve and changes the title. The amendment requires
3322 the Department of Transportation, by December 3, 2025, to submit to the Joint Standing
3333 Committee on Transportation a report detailing its progress on implementing the
3344 recommendations from the 2025 Public Transit Advisory Council report, including specific
3355 dates of actions taken toward implementing those recommendations and specific dates on
